OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMental health: Ex-soldier  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbuilds castle to help      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fveterans with PTSD         
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A former homeless veteran with         
OL,6, post-traumatic stress disorder has     
OL,7, built a castle in which he runs        
OL,8, sessions to help others with their     
OL,9, mental health.                         
OL,11,FMike Allen, 41, from Oakdale,          
OL,12,FCaerphilly, began building it in 2019  
OL,13,Fafter his first cabin was demolished   
OL,14,Fdue to a lack of planning consent.     
OL,16,FOther veterans and stone-wall          
OL,17,Fspecialists helped build the new castle
OL,18,Fby hand, using stone and damaged trees.
OL,20,FIt is now home to Endex, a charitable  
OL,21,Fproject run by Mr Allen.               
